cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DL 

This paper focuses on natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict revision improvement in student essays. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning models, which suggests it could also belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with information retrieval, as it extracts revisions from a dataset, which could place it in the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning, which could place it in the sub-category of Deep Learning (cs.DL).
